Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:04.46,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不 是因为博士太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.90,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,安娜喜欢他是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:09.95,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.54,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,给我命中 给我命中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:47.70,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:52.34,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,这样憎恨他的大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.76,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,和这样冷静的罗安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:56.88,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,把他从危机中救了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:58.34,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:00.73,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:07.44,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,现在 他们的心在彼此交流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:12.62,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我感觉得到 他们为了活下去而向前跨出了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:17.66,Layzner_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}叫他…英二！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.72,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,太好了 大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:41.96,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你们随便就出动太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.17,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.00,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,可是等我回过神来已经坐在机动兵器上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.97,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:53.95,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不过身为男人 在那种情况下有这种反应也是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.63,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,话说回来 为什么在敌人面前把武器丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.63,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,故障了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.57,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不 不是故障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.45,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你说什么 如果不是故障的话 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:14.66,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.95,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,他没有再多说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:25.72,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我感觉到了 沉默道出了他的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:35.70,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:42.00,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我在做报告书 你来告诉我们地球的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:43.60,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.39,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,按那个按键就开始录音了 也会顺便录像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:50.82,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,看着监视器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.48,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,如果把这事好好地记录在报告书上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.67,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,有一天说不定能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:58.95,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.73,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,他为了叫我们坐上机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.30,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,才故意把武器丢掉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.10,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,他不像是会做这种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.27,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:22.20,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 有一天我们总是要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.63,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那种事就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.31,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,话说回来 罗安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.28,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你的行动还蛮好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.71,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我本来以为你只是个眼镜仔而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.65,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.41,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我可是网球部部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.61,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我的运动神经很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.95,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你们真的今后也要战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.61,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,为了要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:49.76,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,比起某人只会在那闲晃 想些有的没的就被杀了 我实在看不惯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.88,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我才不是闲晃想些有的没的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:57.97,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,只是我觉得我技术还不够成熟 如果乱来就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.37,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这就是在想些有的没的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.82,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,身为男人 有时就算乱来也要做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.63,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,说的真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.90,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,今天只是你们运气好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.01,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,如果敌人攻过来 你认为真的能赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:14.68,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,对嘛 正式战斗的话你才不可能赢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.96,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,怎...怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.11,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,正式战斗也随便打就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.16,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,罗安 麻烦把头盔给我 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:24.89,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.49,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,真是单纯的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.89,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没错 我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.91,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,竟然认为有勇无谋就叫男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.70,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你也真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:48.03,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,如果你是男人 不想输给大卫的话就让他看看你的骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.19,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.36,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,欸什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:53.41,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你也去模拟战如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.32,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,对 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:07.23,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,没一个像样的男人 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.72,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:24.25,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二训练地球人驾驶SPT了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.15,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.67,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,我的作战计划太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.22,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,被教训了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.50,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:42.31,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,少尉 地球人的技术很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.48,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,是我大意 我无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.64,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,现在我觉得十分惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.82,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,中尉 请再给我一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.50,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,我一定要发挥中尉您指导的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:01.89,Default_Sub,PilotA,0,0,0,,喂 听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:03.84,Default_Sub,PilotB,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.35,Default_Sub,A,0,0,0,,卡露拉少尉好像还蛮爱面子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.72,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,是之前的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:09.90,Default_Sub,A,0,0,0,,对 她好像在吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:13.41,Default_Sub,A,0,0,0,,因为中尉的恋人是那个叛徒的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.12,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,哇 被打中了 不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.81,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.81,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不行 太难啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.38,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,瞄准敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:37.38,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,命中敌人 摧毁敌人 发射时机0.0050秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.22,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:47.67,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,命中关节部 误差0.02 部位差0.002
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.33,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:49.89,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:53.06,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,他的准心都瞄准哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.30,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,关节部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.48,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,他不打致命伤部位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:02.67,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,他最常打的位置 关节部跟辅助喷射器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:07.95,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,又是脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.63,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你也发现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.19,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,谁都会发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:23.04,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,那个影像是他到目前战斗的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:26.42,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我刚查过了 都有一个共同点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.71,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,他都没打敌人的致命伤 竟还能活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.19,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:35.49,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不过这么一来 就知道他那时丢掉武器的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.95,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,伤脑筋 果然我还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:47.34,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,怎么了 你去练习了啊 是西蒙尼叫你去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.13,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:51.57,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,她对你有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.63,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.45,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,就是对你有意思才会鞭策你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:09:00.04,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你又随便乱说了 男生跟女生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:04.37,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不可能说你叫我去做我就做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.63,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不过为了今后我还是把操纵练熟一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:09.67,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.65,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那家伙认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.95,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:17.34,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,他一直都很悲观 让他有个希望也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.32,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.56,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你们刚才在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.01,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:21.73,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:38.18,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,是炖牛肉 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.14,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,安娜来一下 看我发现了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:41.54,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.65,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.12,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这箱子里什么都有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:53.41,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,古拉多斯对地球人在太空发展军事感到威胁 因此准备攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:10:02.71,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,现在 古拉多斯准备在地球在太空的威胁扩大前 让地球人内讧并征服地球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.30,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,让地球人内讧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:11.28,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,一直以来为地球人所忽略的事 却让远方的外星人感到威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:12.55,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.87,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,呐 你喜欢谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:19.84,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,我是指在这的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:22.09,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,突然被你这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.95,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你应该有想过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.04,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,可是 我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.59,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,那西蒙尼你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.90,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,我？不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.40,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,全部不是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:38.63,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,亚瑟不可靠 大卫爱耍帅 罗安比我小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:39.56,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,那那个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:42.30,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你说他？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:43.75,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.81,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,安娜你喜欢他 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.72,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,觉得一直穿这样好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.98,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.14,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你也脱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.70,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.10,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,把这里面的背包改变一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:16.15,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,他说这样就可以改变 对陆地、空中和宇宙的适应性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.38,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你还真行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:45.88,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这样可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.07,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你也脱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.02,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,可以自由活动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.03,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,太空食物都吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.82,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,有时也要吃吃人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.78,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这味道是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:28.79,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:29.56,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.62,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:37.69,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:41.10,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好久没吃到热的食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:41.75,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:42.96,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不能偷吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.02,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,吃一下有什么问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:51.05,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这东西是用罐头跟冷冻食物等很多东西辛苦做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:53.99,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,要穿正式的服装才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:57.63,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,像你们那身野蛮的太空服 我们火星餐厅不欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:02.70,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,西蒙尼 你应该很清楚我们的处境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:05.53,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,敌人不知道什么时候会来 可是你却...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.56,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不要说那种无聊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:12.23,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,中世纪的贵族 即使在战争中还是会盛装参加餐会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:16.62,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那是中世纪的贵族 跟现在的我们处境又不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:19.21,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你真的什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:25.30,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,亚瑟 西蒙尼是因为不知道明天会怎么样 才说现在要快乐的享受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.74,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,原来如此 好 我赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.78,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,嗯 很合理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:34.79,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,对啊 我也觉得这身装扮不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:46.30,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,请去那边换衣服 这里有吃的 打翻就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:50.90,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,今天就到这吧 差不多该吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:51.38,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.83,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,你们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.32,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,欢迎来到火星餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.76,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,博士 本餐厅禁止正式服装以外的装扮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.50,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,那么我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.14,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.18,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.62,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.78,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,不 因为博士你太漂亮了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.19,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,对啊 你也脱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:29.97,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.92,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,对啊 快把那臭死人的太空服脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.69,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,大家快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.71,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,亚瑟你也去帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:38.53,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,住 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.40,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:40.76,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:43.86,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,住手 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.13,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,好了 英二 不要反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.74,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,亚瑟 快把他的鞋子脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.79,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不要这么不坦率嘛 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:59.11,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,大家不知何时开始叫他英二了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:10.71,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,好久没这样了 忘记何时敌人会来的紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.91,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,在轻松的话题中用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.98,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,博士也很放松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.96,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,露出了一点胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:23.38,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,还有 我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.33,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,头一次看到他的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.72,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,还能再来一碗吗 西蒙尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.94,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,好啊 还有很多 自己来别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.95,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不行 他会吃光的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.20,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,西蒙尼 你帮他弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.38,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,西蒙尼 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:16.12,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,930)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}迪马修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:19.10,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,开始攻击 请放出干扰电波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.28,Default_Sub,Gail(?),0,0,0,,我知道了 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.28,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.51,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,阻止我们也没用 让我们一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.79,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我知道了 但战斗中要听我指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:33.81,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.36,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:36.74,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:40.53,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没事的 这里有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:41.53,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.97,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,那你保护他们两个去通信室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.35,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我去运输船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.01,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.00,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:54.94,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,报告状况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:57.83,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,有三架SPT从上空快速入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.89,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,只有这样而已吗 之前明明还有地面用机器人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.39,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我准备好可以出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.55,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我先出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.28,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,等一下 大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.70,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,罗安 你别过来 原地保护运输船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.61,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.06,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫 停下 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:19.70,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.30,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,有干扰电波
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.43,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.15,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫 你听到了吗 大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.61,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这是特别针对技术不熟练的 他们两人的作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:31.54,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,是以对付他们为主的作战方式 这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:33.30,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.41,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这是什么 怎么了 坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.73,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 听得到吗 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.20,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,因为电波干扰 无法使用无线电
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:44.34,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,冷静 要冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:44.84,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.70,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,来了 这次一定干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:58.62,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.86,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,想逃是吗 不让你逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.34,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,住手 不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.67,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,真讨厌 这么安静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.16,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,听得到吗 罗安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:43.02,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,930)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}布鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.96,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,930)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}多特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:54.34,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,有三架...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.10,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,越想说不要慌就越慌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.54,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,罗安 运输船不重要 快启动逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.22,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,往哪逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.71,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这样下去罗安会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.20,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不想办法不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.39,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:39.60,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,亚瑟！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.87,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,没有炮吗 要按哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:45.58,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,请按右边的按键
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.16,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,哪一个键才能发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.04,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,请按黄色键
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.71,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,博士 我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.30,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:25.58,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,930)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}贝布鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:31.17,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你想逃到哪 来跟我打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.35,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,剩下的两架跑去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.97,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,没事嘛 他们根本都不打过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.61,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,上方有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.17,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,上方是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:50.76,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,下方有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:52.15,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不好了 下面也有是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.51,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.00,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:39.42,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,情报信息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.94,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,母舰有特别电波进入 干扰电波解除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:43.95,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.79,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,少尉 终止作战 马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:50.24,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,为什么 中尉 还差一点我就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.85,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,这是命令 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:55.61,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,中尉 果然你对英二还是有特别的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:56.72,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:57.67,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:02.96,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,好像是地球的太空船往这来了 这里没人保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:04.27,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.69,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,听到了没 少尉 卡露拉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.60,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,了解 马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:23.03,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,走了 他们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:24.17,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:30.13,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,为什么 他们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:35.69,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,亚瑟 你来得正是时候 托你的福得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.69,0:22:36.78,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:38.38,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,罗安 你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:40.25,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.47,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,这时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:50.17,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,根本就不知道 有地球的太空船接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.07,0:23:56.21,Default_Sub,Trailer,0,0,0,,地球的船?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:57.53,Default_Sub,Trailer,0,0,0,,是军舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:23:58.75,Default_Sub,Trailer,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:00.37,Default_Sub,Trailer,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.07,Default_Sub,Trailer,0,0,0,,外星人的机动部队接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.07,0:24:03.29,Default_Sub,Trailer,0,0,0,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:04.51,Default_Sub,Trailer,0,0,0,,不要让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:09.09,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\c&HE5E8DC&\pos(720,770)}地球的船来了！
